translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Enough, you don't have to eat anymore."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Neesan, aren’t you being too lenient with Noir and Nogiku?"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Now is the time for Noir and Masamune to be lovey-dovey."
